'''1962年美國職棒大聯盟全明星賽第二場'''是[[大聯盟|大聯盟]]歷史上第33屆全明星賽，比賽於{{mlby|1962}}7月30日在[[芝加哥小熊|芝加哥小熊]]的主場瑞格利球場舉行。這場比賽美聯以9比4打敗國聯，拿下明星賽勝利。<ref name=autogenerated1>{{Cite web |url=http://www.baseball-almanac.com/asgbox/yr1962as.shtml |title=1962 All-Star Game<!-- Bot generated title --> |accessdate=2020-08-13 |archive-date=2020-06-11 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200611105020/https://baseball-almanac.com/asgbox/yr1962as.shtml |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{Cite web |url=http://mlb.mlb.com/mlb/history/mlb_asgrecaps_story_headline.jsp?story_page=recap_1962a |title=All-Star Game Recaps {{!}} MLB.com: History<!-- Bot generated title --> |accessdate=2020-08-13 |archive-date=2020-11-15 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201115054630/http://mlb.mlb.com/mlb/history/mlb_asgrecaps_story_headline.jsp?story_page=recap_1962a |dead-url=no }}</ref>這年因為明星賽舉辦滿30週年，因此大聯盟於該年設置明星賽MVP獎項。Maury Wills拿下第一場的MVP，Leon Wagner拿下第二場的MVP。<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://mlb.mlb.com/news/article.jsp?ymd=20060710&content_id=1550905&vkey=allstar2006&fext=.jsp |title=All-Star MVP awaits your vote {{!}} MLB.com: News<!-- Bot generated title --> |accessdate=2020-08-13 |archive-date=2014-03-26 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140326102953/http://mlb.mlb.com/news/article.jsp?ymd=20060710&content_id=1550905&vkey=allstar2006&fext=.jsp |dead-url=no }}</ref>

